---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import SiteNav from '../../components/SiteNav.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer';
---

<Layout
  title="How Pricing Works | Intent Solutions"
  description="Transparent pricing by design. Flat platform fee + usage at provider list prices. No vendor lock-in."
>
  <SiteNav />

  <main class="bg-zinc-900">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="py-24 border-b border-zinc-800/60">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-8">
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
          <p class="uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 mb-4">
            education
          </p>
          <h1 class="text-h1 font-bold text-zinc-50 mb-6">
            how pricing works
          </h1>
          <p class="text-lg text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
            Transparent by design. Flat platform fee + usage at provider list prices. No lock-in,
            full portability.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Engagement Ladder -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-zinc-950 border-b border-zinc-800/60">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-8">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-50 mb-8">engagement ladder</h2>

          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 rounded-lg p-6">
              <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between mb-2">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-100">discovery sprint</h3>
                <span class="text-sm text-zinc-400">1–2 weeks</span>
              </div>
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-50 mb-3">$1,500</div>
              <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 mb-3">
                <strong className="text-zinc-300">Deliverables:</strong> Architecture diagram,
                prioritized backlog, rollout plan with risk assessment.
              </p>
              <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500">
                Validates technical feasibility, scopes MVP, and sets expectations before build.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 rounded-lg p-6">
              <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between mb-2">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-100">mvp build</h3>
                <span class="text-sm text-zinc-400">2–6 weeks</span>
              </div>
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-50 mb-3">$8K–$25K fixed-bid typical</div>
              <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 mb-3">
                <strong className="text-zinc-300">Scope-dependent.</strong> Includes deployment,
                testing, documentation, and team training handoff.
              </p>
              <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500">
                Price varies by data integrations, compliance requirements, and custom logic
                complexity.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 rounded-lg p-6">
              <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between mb-2">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-100">managed service</h3>
                <span class="text-sm text-zinc-400">flat + usage</span>
              </div>
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-50 mb-3">from $1,497/mo</div>
              <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 mb-3">
                <strong className="text-zinc-300">Includes:</strong> Platform operations,
                monitoring, on-call support, first quota of search queries and index storage.
              </p>
              <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500">
                Usage beyond included quota billed at provider list prices. See "What drives
                usage" below.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 rounded-lg p-6">
              <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between mb-2">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-100">enterprise private ai</h3>
                <span class="text-sm text-zinc-400">+ infrastructure</span>
              </div>
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-50 mb-3">from $3,000/mo</div>
              <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 mb-3">
                <strong className="text-zinc-300">Includes:</strong> Dedicated infrastructure,
                priority support (1-hour SLA), compliance documentation, monthly optimization
                reviews.
              </p>
              <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500">
                Custom pricing for multi-region, high-volume, or specialized compliance needs.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- What Drives Usage -->
    <section class="py-24 border-b border-zinc-800/60">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-8">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-50 mb-8">what drives usage</h2>

          <div class="bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
            <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-4">
              We use a flat platform fee to cover managed operations, monitoring, and support. We
              include a clear quota for monthly usage. Beyond that, usage is billed at provider
              list prices for search, storage, models, and network. You can bring your own cloud
              accounts. Budgets are enforced with caps, alerts, and prepaid blocks.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800 rounded-lg p-6">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-3">queries & invocations</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-zinc-400">
                <li>• Search API calls (vector, hybrid, keyword)</li>
                <li>• Model inference requests</li>
                <li>• Tool and function executions</li>
                <li>• Workflow orchestration steps</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800 rounded-lg p-6">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-3">storage</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-zinc-400">
                <li>• Vector index storage (per GB)</li>
                <li>• Document and artifact storage</li>
                <li>• Backup and snapshot retention</li>
                <li>• Log and audit trail storage</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800 rounded-lg p-6">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-3">compute</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-zinc-400">
                <li>• Batch embedding jobs</li>
                <li>• Scheduled evaluation runs</li>
                <li>• Data transformation pipelines</li>
                <li>• Custom processing workflows</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800 rounded-lg p-6">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-3">network & quality ops</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-zinc-400">
                <li>• Downstream API calls (egress)</li>
                <li>• Third-party integrations</li>
                <li>• Evaluation and testing runs</li>
                <li>• Incident response budget</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Example MVP Bundle -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-zinc-950 border-b border-zinc-800/60">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-8">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-50 mb-8">example mvp bundle</h2>

          <div class="bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 rounded-lg p-8">
            <div class="mb-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-4">
                monthly fee includes:
              </h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-zinc-400">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                  </svg>
                  <span>Managed platform operations, monitoring, and on-call support</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                  </svg>
                  <span>First 10,000 search queries per month</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                  </svg>
                  <span>Up to 50GB index storage</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                  </svg>
                  <span>Basic monthly reports and dashboards</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="border-t border-zinc-800 pt-6">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-3">
                usage beyond included quota:
              </h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
                Billed at provider list prices for search, storage, models, and network. Provider
                can be swapped per client policy. No markup—we pass through provider pricing
                directly.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Budget Controls -->
    <section class="py-24 border-b border-zinc-800/60">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-8">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-50 mb-8">budget controls</h2>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div class="card-slate">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">prepaid blocks</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
                Purchase usage credits in advance with volume discounts. Alerts when balance runs
                low.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="card-slate">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">per-workspace caps</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
                Set spending limits per team, project, or environment. Hard caps prevent overruns.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="card-slate">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">monthly rollups</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
                Detailed usage breakdowns by service, workspace, and time period. Export for
                chargeback.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="card-slate">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">live dashboards</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
                Real-time cost tracking with forecasting. See spend trends and optimize before
                month-end.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Portability -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-zinc-950">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-8">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-50 mb-8">portability & lock-in prevention</h2>

          <div class="bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 rounded-lg p-8">
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">
                  bring-your-own cloud keys
                </h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
                  Use your own Google Cloud, AWS, or Azure accounts. We never hold your data
                  hostage.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">
                  export data and indexes anytime
                </h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
                  Full data export in standard formats. Indexes can be migrated to other platforms.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">
                  switch providers without rebuild
                </h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
                  Model-agnostic architecture means you can swap Claude for OpenAI, Gemini for
                  Llama, without code rewrites.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-8 text-center">
            <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-6">
              Questions about pricing or want a custom quote?
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center">
              <a href="/#contact" class="btn-primary">
                discuss your use case
              </a>
              <a
                href="/learn"
                class="inline-flex items-center text-zinc-200 hover:text-zinc-50 transition-smooth"
              >
                ← back to learn hub
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
